{
  "stem": "21652.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Healthy men and women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were broken people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were just nearing the end, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, beds, barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were the lucky ones to have beds, because the remaining girls stayed in that room, and most of them died.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A very small percentage of the 150 girls survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow, I apparently improved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My health improved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then my sister, Esther, succumbed to the sickness, high fever, and diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was feeling better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my sister, Mary, was still in between.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I heard rumors the war ended.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The English are here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went to tell my sister, who was lying sick.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, Esther, we are liberated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The English are here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It didn't make an impression on her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was kind of far gone, it seems.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But later-- later on, she regained consciousness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Her health improved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were told that our brother is in the same camp, our brother, Simon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because there were lists of surviving people looking for one another.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Even in Bergen-Belsen, in the camp, there were lists of names.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then one girl came to tell my sister and told her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that woke her up-- that Simon is alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she regained consciousness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then we were told that they're waiting for us behind barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were kind of freed, and they had freedom of movement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we did not realize that we were free, and we were too sick--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To leave.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To leave.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were told at that point that they poisoned the water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had the English not arrived on that day-- I think it was April, the latter part of April or middle part-- that we would all have died.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans poisoned the water.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
